# Blog Posts Directory

Add your markdown (.md) files here. Each file should include frontmatter with:
- title: Blog post title
- date: Publication date (YYYY-MM-DD)
- excerpt: Short description
- author: Author name (optional)
- category: Category name (optional)
- tags: Array of tags (optional)
- image: Featured image URL (optional)

Example:

---
title: "How to Keep Your Pet Healthy"
date: "2025-01-15"
excerpt: "Learn essential tips for maintaining your pet's health and wellbeing."
author: "Dr. Sarah Johnson"
category: "Health"
tags: ["health", "wellness", "tips"]
image: "/images/blog/pet-health.jpg"
---

Your blog content here in markdown format...

